I'm very glad that I don't
have to sit on that panel, son.

01:54:45.994 --> 01:54:47.951
You made it
awful tough on them.

01:54:51.327 --> 01:54:53.904
- 15,000 to 25,000...
- Excuse me.

01:54:58.489 --> 01:55:00.406
I said no interruptions.

01:55:00.486 --> 01:55:03.443
