what the life expectancy was...

01:58:45.910 --> 01:58:50.234
for a second lieutenant dropped
into a hot L.Z. in Vietnam in 1968,

01:58:50.324 --> 01:58:53.241
I'll tell you everything
I remember about Ca Lu.

01:58:54.739 --> 01:58:56.277
- One week.
- Negative.

01:58:56.367 --> 01:58:59.613
Sixteen minutes, Major.

01:58:59.693 --> 01:59:02.530
Sixteen fucking minutes.

01:59:02.570 --> 01:59:04.567
And that's all I remember.

01:59:53.060 --> 01:59:55.058
Sir.

01:59:57.000 --> 02:00:02.973
William Sokal was found guilty of destroying evidence.

02:00:03.073 --> 02:00:06.951
He was forced to resign as the National Security advisor.

02:00:07.051 --> 02:00:13.078
Ambassador Mourain was dismissed from the diplomatic corp. He was charged with perjury.

02:00:13.878 --> 02:00:18.472
There was no further charges against General Colonel Terry Childers.

02:00:18.772 --> 02:00:22.373
He retired with full military honors from the Marine Corps.
